long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Waywire Publisher Chrome Extension is a free service for Waywire Enterprise customers. Waywire's video curation functionality is consolidated into one neat, easy-to-access pop-out window, enabling you to search for videos without leaving the webpage you are visiting. You can add content to your library and quickly retrieve embed codes with just the click of a button.
